<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 12:11:08 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>释放我儿子的巴勒斯坦杀手，以释放哈马斯扣押的以色列人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article-opinion/.premium/free-my-sons-palestinian-killer-to-free-the-israeli-hostages-held-by-hamas/0000018c-76ce-db38-a9fc-ffee21580000</link><description>只要婴儿、父亲、母亲和兄弟仍被困在加沙，整个以色列都是哈马斯的人质，人质家庭的处境最为严重。这就是为什么我呼吁释放杀害我心爱儿子的狙击手，如果这能带回他们的亲人之一</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 11:43:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article-opinion/.premium/free-my-sons-palestinian-killer-to-free-the-israeli-hostages-held-by-hamas/0000018c-76ce-db38-a9fc-ffee21580000</guid></item><item><title>以色列枪支许可机构负责人表示，本-格维尔的政策导致“失控”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/head-of-israels-gun-licensing-authority-ben-gvirs-policy-leading-to-loss-of-control/0000018c-767f-db38-a9fc-fffffa160000</link><description>负责批准枪支许可证的以色列官员敦促极右翼部长改变其政策，因为有消息称本-格维尔的同伙已被任命在未经必要授权的情况下处理请求</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 11:14:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/head-of-israels-gun-licensing-authority-ben-gvirs-policy-leading-to-loss-of-control/0000018c-767f-db38-a9fc-fffffa160000</guid></item><item><title>五名巴勒斯坦人在约旦河西岸丧生，四人死于以色列军队无人机袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/five-palestinians-killed-in-west-bank-four-from-israeli-army-drone-strike/0000018c-7731-dabb-afae-77b355360000</link><description>这次袭击是在巴勒斯坦城市图尔卡尔姆连夜进行的，是以色列国防军自战争开始以来在该地区第二次“制止恐怖”行动之际进行的</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 11:02:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/five-palestinians-killed-in-west-bank-four-from-israeli-army-drone-strike/0000018c-7731-dabb-afae-77b355360000</guid></item><item><title>法国外交部称工人在以色列对加沙拉法的袭击中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/french-foreign-ministry-says-worker-killed-by-an-israeli-strike-in-gazas-rafah/0000018c-7724-dbd5-a39c-ff772e860000</link><description>法国外交部表示，我们要求以色列当局尽快全面了解这次爆炸事件的情况。</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 09:47:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/french-foreign-ministry-says-worker-killed-by-an-israeli-strike-in-gazas-rafah/0000018c-7724-dbd5-a39c-ff772e860000</guid></item><item><title>半岛电视台将以色列袭击导致加沙摄影师死亡案件移交国际刑事法院</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/al-jazeera-to-refer-death-of-cameraman-in-gaza-from-israeli-strike-to-icc/0000018c-76e1-dbd5-a39c-fff376d80000</link><description>据半岛电视台报道，摄影师萨米尔·阿布·达卡 (Samer Abu Daqqa) 在报道早些时候对加沙学校的爆炸事件时在以色列无人机袭击中身亡。以色列国防军表示“从未”故意针对记者</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 09:24:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/al-jazeera-to-refer-death-of-cameraman-in-gaza-from-israeli-strike-to-icc/0000018c-76e1-dbd5-a39c-fff376d80000</guid></item><item><title>来自黎巴嫩的导弹瞄准以色列基布兹；两名以色列国防军士兵在加沙战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article-live/idf-names-two-reserve-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-combat-palestinians-two-killed-in-w-bank/0000018c-75f4-db38-a9fc-fdf659620000</link><description>以色列国防军公布了两名在加沙战斗中丧生的士兵的名字 ■ 巴勒斯坦人报告称，五人在西岸图尔卡姆附近的以色列无人机袭击中丧生 ■ 美国国防部长启程前往以色列 ■ 来自黎巴嫩的反坦克导弹击中以色列北部基布兹的建筑物 ■ 至少 1,200 名平民和自 10 月 7 日以来，以色列士兵被杀；加沙至少有 130 名人质被扣押 ■ 哈马斯卫生部：加沙 18,608 人死亡，50,594 人受伤</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 04:31:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article-live/idf-names-two-reserve-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-combat-palestinians-two-killed-in-w-bank/0000018c-75f4-db38-a9fc-fdf659620000</guid></item><item><title>据《纽约时报》报道，以色列在发现哈马斯价值 5 亿美元的资产后没有采取行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/israel-failed-to-act-after-finding-hamas-assets-worth-half-a-billion-dollars-nyt-reports/0000018c-74e3-d48b-a5ec-74f382e00000</link><description>自 2018 年以来，以色列和美国高级官员都知道详细介绍哈马斯网络的秘密文件，价值数亿美元，目前据信这些文件为 10 月 7 日的袭击提供了资金</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 02:44:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/israel-failed-to-act-after-finding-hamas-assets-worth-half-a-billion-dollars-nyt-reports/0000018c-74e3-d48b-a5ec-74f382e00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人质在雷伊姆附近的聚会中被绑架，在囚禁期间被哈马斯谋杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostage-kidnapped-from-party-near-reim-murdered-by-hamas-while-in-captivity/0000018c-749a-d48b-a5ec-74dbea7f0000</link><description>27 岁的因巴尔·海曼 (Inbar Haiman) 成功躲避哈马斯恐怖分子两个小时，然后于 10 月 7 日被拖到加沙。她是一名涂鸦艺术家，正在学习视觉传达</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 01:55:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostage-kidnapped-from-party-near-reim-murdered-by-hamas-while-in-captivity/0000018c-749a-d48b-a5ec-74dbea7f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列南部贝都因小镇男子被枪杀，警方正在调查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/man-shot-to-death-in-southern-israeli-bedouin-town-police-investigating/0000018c-7541-dbd5-a39c-ff7371ad0000</link><description>以色列警方怀疑这名 29 岁的男子因家庭不和而被枪杀。这起谋杀案是本周末发生的第三起疑似谋杀案</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 01:38:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/man-shot-to-death-in-southern-israeli-bedouin-town-police-investigating/0000018c-7541-dbd5-a39c-ff7371ad0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方逮捕两人并驱散以色列北部的反加沙战争抗议活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-arrest-two-disperse-anti-gaza-war-protest-in-northern-israel/0000018c-7496-d48b-a5ec-74d7d0d70000</link><description>参加示威的人数不到20人，但现场有很多警察。一名被拘留的抗议者说，我们站在那里进行合法的抗议守夜活动，没有打扰任何人。</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 00:43:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-arrest-two-disperse-anti-gaza-war-protest-in-northern-israel/0000018c-7496-d48b-a5ec-74d7d0d70000</guid></item><item><title>获释人质在特拉维夫集会上发表讲话，要求释放协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/freed-hostages-address-tel-aviv-rally-to-demand-release-deal/0000018c-7467-dbd5-a39c-ff77679f0000</link><description>“我们警告说，战斗可能会伤害人质。不幸的是，我们是对的，”以色列军队在加沙战斗中误杀三名人质后，一名被释放的人质说道</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 Dec 2023 22:37:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/freed-hostages-address-tel-aviv-rally-to-demand-release-deal/0000018c-7467-dbd5-a39c-ff77679f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的两个战争目标发生致命冲突，加沙的每一天都让人质面临危险</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-16/ty-article/.premium/israels-two-war-aims-meet-for-a-fatal-clash-every-day-in-gaza-endangers-hostages/0000018c-73d3-d798-adac-f7ff8ca30000</link><description>地面入侵加沙已经六周了，很难看出所有人质的返回和哈马斯的毁灭这两个目标如何同时实现。尽管家人提出要求，以色列并不急于恢复与哈马斯的谈判</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 Dec 2023 19:53:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-16/ty-article/.premium/israels-two-war-aims-meet-for-a-fatal-clash-every-day-in-gaza-endangers-hostages/0000018c-73d3-d798-adac-f7ff8ca30000</guid></item><item><title>在加沙被以色列国防军杀害的贝都因以色列人质的家人在葬礼后指责以色列和哈马斯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-16/ty-article/.premium/after-funeral-of-bedouin-israeli-hostage-killed-by-idf-family-blames-israel-and-hamas/0000018c-7369-d798-adac-f7effe1e0000</link><description>被以色列国防军误杀的三名人质之一萨米尔·塔拉尔卡的葬礼于周六举行。他的父亲说，以色列军队必须“从所发生的事情中吸取教训”。萨默应该和我们在一起”</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 Dec 2023 17:25:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-16/ty-article/.premium/after-funeral-of-bedouin-israeli-hostage-killed-by-idf-family-blames-israel-and-hamas/0000018c-7369-d798-adac-f7effe1e0000</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，摩萨德负责人在欧洲会见卡塔尔总理，讨论以色列与哈马斯的人质交易</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-16/ty-article/.premium/mossad-chief-met-qatari-pm-in-europe-to-discuss-israel-hamas-hostage-deal-source-says/0000018c-7359-dbd5-a39c-ff7b9ac90000</link><description>以色列战时内阁将于周六召开会议，讨论继续接触的问题，但知情人士表示，以色列和哈马斯距离达成新协议还很遥远。据报道，摩萨德负责人还可能会见埃及高级官员</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 Dec 2023 16:40:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-16/ty-article/.premium/mossad-chief-met-qatari-pm-in-europe-to-discuss-israel-hamas-hostage-deal-source-says/0000018c-7359-dbd5-a39c-ff7b9ac90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军初步报告：被士兵杀害的人质挥舞着白旗，其中一人用希伯来语呼救</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-16/ty-article/.premium/preliminary-idf-report-hostages-killed-by-soldiers-waved-white-flag-yelled-help-hebrew/0000018c-7283-db38-a9fc-fba363100000</link><description>报道称，悲剧发生两天前，以色列士兵在该地区发现了一栋建筑物，上面写着“SOS”和“救命！”在其中一堵墙上。以色列国防军部队在将该建筑物标记为可能的陷阱的区域行动</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 Dec 2023 12:29:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-16/ty-article/.premium/preliminary-idf-report-hostages-killed-by-soldiers-waved-white-flag-yelled-help-hebrew/0000018c-7283-db38-a9fc-fba363100000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗称已处决以色列摩萨德特工</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-12-16/ty-article/iran-says-it-has-executed-an-israeli-mossad-spy/0000018c-7215-d798-adac-f6bfbe9f0000</link><description>伊朗官方媒体称，这名身份不明的男子与摩萨德等外国情报机构有联系，并被指控参与泄露机密信息</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 Dec 2023 10:13:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-12-16/ty-article/iran-says-it-has-executed-an-israeli-mossad-spy/0000018c-7215-d798-adac-f6bfbe9f0000</guid></item><item><title>三名以色列人质被以色列国防军误杀后，数百人在特拉维夫集会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-16/ty-article/.premium/hundreds-of-israelis-rally-in-tel-aviv-calling-for-immediate-release-of-hostages/0000018c-71c6-db38-a9fc-f9e608ee0000</link><description>以色列士兵在加沙悲惨地杀害了三名人质，原因是他们被误认为是哈马斯成员，数百人走上特拉维夫街头，呼吁政府重返谈判桌并与哈马斯达成协议</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 Dec 2023 09:33:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-16/ty-article/.premium/hundreds-of-israelis-rally-in-tel-aviv-calling-for-immediate-release-of-hostages/0000018c-71c6-db38-a9fc-f9e608ee0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军：两名士兵在加沙丧生；以色列人呼吁在特拉维夫达成释放人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-16/ty-article-live/hundreds-protest-in-tel-aviv-after-three-hamas-hostages-mistakenly-killed-by-idf/0000018c-707c-d798-adac-f4ff14b20000</link><description>以色列国防军在加沙误杀三名人质后，以色列人走上街头；以色列国防军负责人声称对死亡事件负责 ■ 加沙武装分子在地面行动中丧生 ■ 以色列国防军士兵在来自黎巴嫩的无人机袭击中丧生；以色列国防军袭击真主党目标 ■ 摩萨德主席在欧洲会见卡塔尔总理，讨论新的人质协议 ■ 航运巨头因胡塞武装袭击而暂停红海交通 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，以色列至少有 1,200 名平民和士兵丧生；加沙至少有 130 名人质被扣押 ■ 哈马斯卫生部：加沙 18,608 人死亡，50,594 人受伤</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 Dec 2023 02:52:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-16/ty-article-live/hundreds-protest-in-tel-aviv-after-three-hamas-hostages-mistakenly-killed-by-idf/0000018c-707c-d798-adac-f4ff14b20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列可以从纽约 9/11 清理和纪念活动中学到什么</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-16/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/what-israel-can-learn-from-new-yorks-9-11-cleanup-and-commemoration/0000018c-6f95-db38-a9fc-efb71e8b0000</link><description>以色列不应该清除南部 10 月 7 日灾难的废墟，而应该学习纽约在 9 月 11 日之后所做的事情</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 23:20:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-16/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/what-israel-can-learn-from-new-yorks-9-11-cleanup-and-commemoration/0000018c-6f95-db38-a9fc-efb71e8b0000</guid></item><item><title>如果定居者的暴力还不够，以色列现在正在剥夺约旦河谷巴勒斯坦人的水源</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2023-12-16/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/if-settler-violence-wasnt-enough-israel-now-deprives-jordan-valley-palestinians-of-water/0000018c-6f70-dbd5-a39c-ff7344530000</link><description>自战争爆发以来，约 20 个巴勒斯坦家庭因定居者暴力加剧而被迫离开约旦河谷的家园。与此同时，军队不让牧羊人社区获得水源。以色列志愿者日夜努力保护他们</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 22:24:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2023-12-16/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/if-settler-violence-wasnt-enough-israel-now-deprives-jordan-valley-palestinians-of-water/0000018c-6f70-dbd5-a39c-ff7344530000</guid></item></channel></rss>